ten_Affirmation.pdf; FY26_IDEA_Grant_St.Paul_Attestation.pdf; Hingham FY25 Equitable Services Mid Year Monitoring.xlsx.', 'Need exact request text and full attachment review before declaring categories satisfied. Potential gaps if request sought all Hingham communications, consultation records, allocation data, or implementation records.', 'Possible DESE-only custody limitation if records are district-held by Hingham rather than DESE-held.', 'Need verify any redactions, exemptions, search limits, or no-custody language in full response body.', 'Possible scope drift: produced Derby/St. Paul/FY25 monitoring records may be responsive but may not cover full request scope; .msg may contain nested materials.', 'No appeal yet located. Appeal rights language appears in forwarded response.', 'Download linked files into Drive folder; open .msg; compare produced records to exact request categories; consider follow-up to DESE or Hingham RAO.', 'https://mail.google.com/mail/#all/19f4d66f836ac0c1', 'Drive folder: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LHxirKNgup3X1eGLn7Ov7ZT6tZbnObXj ; index doc: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1j2sk-vJKOV9AkiY8ciW43GmgpGSQDf-VYAuHU-qeOhs/edit?usp=drivesdk', 'Medium', 'Response one business day late by date if request was received June 17 and July 3 was not a business day; production itself appears within 25 business days.');